# Compile-time overrides for pip-compile to clear pip-audit.
#
# marker-pdf currently transitively requires:
#   * Pillow<11 (vulnerable; 12.2+ fixed) - moved to optional extra
#   * transformers 4.57.6 (vulnerable; 5.0+ fixed)
#   * markdownify 0.13.1 (vulnerable; 0.14.1 fixed)
# These pins pull the fix versions into the lock until marker-pdf
# ships a clean release. Pillow is unpinned here because we removed
# the marker-pdf transitive coupling; the base image ships Pillow>=12
# directly via the explicit pyproject dependency.
transformers>=5.0.0
markdownify>=0.14.1
